<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="advice-n">advice <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əd'vaɪs/    美 /əd'vaɪs/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>忠告；建议：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a piece of advice</strong> 
一条建议</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>ask / seek sb’s advice / ask sb for advice</strong>
征求某人的意见</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>accept / follow / take sb’s advice</strong> 
接受某人的意见</p></div></div>